    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税对增长、美联储和就业可能意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/what-trump-s-tariffs-could-mean-for-growth-fed-and-jobs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席全球经济学家 Seth Carpenter 在《彭博收盘》中表示，特朗普总统的关税可能会使美国经济增长率下降一个百分点，并对就业构成重大下行风险。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/what-trump-s-tariffs-could-mean-for-growth-fed-and-jobs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:13:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的长期关税策略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/china-s-long-term-tariff-game-plan-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Albright Stonebridge Group 合伙人 Amy Celico 表示，中国政府预计将在与美国的关税谈判中发挥长期作用。她与 Caroline Hyde 和 Jackie Davalos 一起在《彭博科技》节目中讨论这一问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/china-s-long-term-tariff-game-plan-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:08:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>年金销售激增，保险公司争相发行证券化债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/insurers-clamor-for-securitized-debt-as-annuity-sales-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利表示，保险公司正在抢购资产支持债券，为其年金产品的未来支出提供资金，而年金产品的需求正创下历史新高 — — 预计这一趋势将持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/insurers-clamor-for-securitized-debt-as-annuity-sales-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 20:55:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加征关税或导致美国油价上涨 15 美分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-drivers-may-see-pump-prices-jump-15-cents-on-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位石油分析师表示，唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大和墨西哥的石油征收关税可能会导致美国燃油价格每加仑上涨约 15 美分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-drivers-may-see-pump-prices-jump-15-cents-on-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 20:51:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
